{"tid":2049732,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【突發】六四前夕，在華盛頓的天安門民主女神像被塗污","createTime":"2020-06-03T15:44:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-03T23:03:04.000Z","uid":48040,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"cadecc37e2d91dc8b23ef9838852a09b60e5b6ae","tid":2049732,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T15:44:32.000Z","msg":"呢個紀念碑以六四事件中天安門民主女神像為藍本，紀念六四死難者。但被人噴上了BLM（可能係black life matter)字樣，又有人係紀念碑前豎中指。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KzaGSPj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKzaGSPj.jpg&h=f64a8e23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WbzP1H1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWbzP1H1.jpg&h=640815db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/shengxue_ca/status/1267919595073089538?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fshengxue_ca%2Fstatus%2F1267919595073089538%3Fs%3D21&d=ZttPR3oQiG8LQafLEcup%2BAKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=d1fc6a4e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fshengxue_ca%2Fstatus%2F1267919595073089538%3Fs%3D21&h=dc54f41f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/shengxue_ca/status/1267919595073089538?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f6Z8xQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff6Z8xQQ.png&h=a67e319e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%85%B1%E4%BA%A7%E4%B8%BB%E4%B9%89%E5%8F%97%E5%AE%B3%E8%80%85%E7%BA%AA%E5%BF%B5%E9%9B%95%E5%83%8F_(%E5%8D%8E%E7%9B%9B%E9%A1%BF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-tw%2F%25E5%2585%25B1%25E4%25BA%25A7%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E4%25B9%2589%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%25AE%25B3%25E8%2580%2585%25E7%25BA%25AA%25E5%25BF%25B5%25E9%259B%2595%25E5%2583%258F_%28%25E5%258D%258E%25E7%259B%259B%25E9%25A1%25BF&d=ZttPR3oQiG8LQafLEcup%2BAKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=49cad5e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%85%B1%E4%BA%A7%E4%B8%BB%E4%B9%89%E5%8F%97%E5%AE%B3%E8%80%85%E7%BA%AA%E5%BF%B5%E9%9B%95%E5%83%8F_(%E5%8D%8E%E7%9B%9B%E9%A1%BF</a>)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n～～～～～<br />\n黃channel需要大家支持，可以幫手CLS嗎？<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0iBFBs1MH3I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0iBFBs1MH3I&d=ZttPR3oQiG8LQafLEcup%2BAKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=191f9e24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0iBFBs1MH3I</a>"},{"pid":"6ef5d1eb01cb20880dcdf9f688637a1e130d14f3","tid":2049732,"uid":21641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T15:45:04.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"250fe1e357d8d6fe768714f9bca69a0b41958289","tid":2049732,"uid":266503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T15:46:09.000Z","msg":"政權除了要我們恐懼多，還要散佈仇恨同分化民眾。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1065677\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1065677&d=ZttPR3oQiG8LQafLEcup%2BAKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=3934fba8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1065677&h=892f01aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1065677</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「人民不應該害怕他們的政府，政府應該害怕它的人民。」（People should not be afraid of their governments. Governments should be afraid of their people.）<br />\n<br />\n「藝術家用謊言揭露真相，政治家用謊言掩蓋真相。」（Artists use lies to tell the truth, while politicians use them to cover the truth up.）<br />\n<br />\n「沒有舞蹈的革命，是不值得發動的革命。」（A revolution without dancing is a revolution not worth having）<br />\n<br />\n「面具之下只是個血肉之軀，而在這面具之下的，還有一個理念，只不過，理念，是刀槍不入的。」（Beneath this mask there is more than flesh. Beneath this mask there is an idea, Mr.Creedy, and ideas are bulletproof..）<br />\n<br />\n「我們的尊嚴可能不值錢，但它卻是我們唯一真正擁有的東西。它是我們最後一寸領地，但在那一寸領地裡，我們是自由的。」（Our integrity sells for so little, but it is all we really have. It is the very last inch of us, but within that inch, we are free）<br />\n<br />\n「力量來自團結，團結來自信念」（Strength through unity, unity through faith）<br />\n<br />\n「恐懼往往是政府的終極武器。」（Fear became the ultimate tool of this government）<br />\n<br />\n「就算政府擁有的武力統治不讓人民發言，自由的言論仍然充滿著強大的力量。」（the truncheon may be used in lieu of conversation, words will always retain their power)"},{"pid":"38597ac8a5a8af4e0cfdf898aa13ebd6857a18bf","tid":2049732,"uid":155818,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T15:46:14.000Z","msg":"D 力架做乜鳩<br />\n又無得罪佢地"},{"pid":"80ec01bd7cfb9464c485426caddadfc6fef9bf0a","tid":2049732,"uid":252142,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38597ac8a5a8af4e0cfdf898aa13ebd6857a18bf","tid":2049732,"uid":155818,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T15:46:14.000Z","msg":"D 力架做乜鳩<br />\n又無得罪佢地"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T15:47:07.000Z","msg":"窮力架收外國勢力錢做野姐"},{"pid":"b6fcb77aca82319f88c878da7bac24e096ac4930","tid":2049732,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T15:47:35.000Z","msg":"佢哋係咪共產黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"751fac3137c2e334a5c8e79225cb9646094a0ab3","tid":2049732,"uid":283912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T15:47:52.000Z","msg":"{拒絕大中華膠}重細節做起,六四抗爭口號上線~<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2049710\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2049710</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"23474bb15b652d80c582e2a9b3d103a2f90311de","tid":2049732,"uid":48040,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"38597ac8a5a8af4e0cfdf898aa13ebd6857a18bf","tid":2049732,"uid":155818,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T15:46:14.000Z","msg":"D 力架做乜鳩<br />\n又無得罪佢地"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T15:54:20.000Z","msg":"因為紀念碑係針對中國"},{"pid":"131acde1d6c254099ab38e90e4a2578a942b203c","tid":2049732,"uid":150483,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"23474bb15b652d80